item.title: Nashville Sounds pay tribute to parent club, beer with new Brewskis cap
item.description: The Triple-A Nashville Sounds have been an affiliate of the Milwaukee Brewers since 2021, and before that from 2005 to 2014. item.title: Denver Broncos’ New Helmet Design Leaks On NFL Draft Prop
item.description: The design of the Denver Broncos' new helmets were leaked by former NFL wide receiver Antonio Brown, who shared a photo on social media of an oversized helmet that will be on display at next week's draft.
